You can edit your collection properties, such as name and description, and also delete the collection altogether. Shared users with the Manager role can also edit and delete the collection.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Group, Enterprise, Professional, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.
Also available with CRM Analytics

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To manage a collection:	Enhanced Folder Sharing, Run Reports AND Create and Customize Dashboards
To manage a collection with CRM Analytics items:	Use CRM Analytics, Edit a collection.

Edit a collection:
Open a collection.
Click the dropdown menu and click Edit.
Add your changes in the Edit Collection window.
Click Save.
Delete a collection:
Open a collection.
Click the dropdown menu and click Delete.
Click Delete again to confirm your action.
title: Editing Collections in Salesforce Analytics
